Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.40,0:02:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.60,0:02:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白晝在逐漸死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.84,0:02:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第六十八話\N命運的墜子\N左之助與小夜的邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.04,0:02:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發出預告狀一再殺人\N自稱神子的人就是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.91,0:03:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼 居然用出怪招術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.58,0:03:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋 你這騙小孩的把戲\N對我行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神算什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.33,0:03:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要剝下你的妖怪之皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招 薄刃之太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.05,0:04:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這劍術是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 救命呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.70,0:04:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 出現了 是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.07,0:04:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白晝轉為黑暗時\N他真的出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 剛才那到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太陽竟然消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.72,0:05:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是神劍創造了奇跡\N翔伍大人創造奇跡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說了 閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇跡？翔伍到底是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.59,0:05:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,張 你聽見沒有 張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.66,0:06:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 是拔刀齊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.37,0:06:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.94,0:06:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼 為什麼你以外的人\N會使用御劍流的招術呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.28,0:06:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 那可能已超越流派了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.68,0:06:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想承認 但…\N我頭一次體驗到那種恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.89,0:06:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是神子？是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.13,0:06:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.83,0:06:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是有一點我敢肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.50,0:06:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊 他比你更強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.84,0:06:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎 他的事你最好別去管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.71,0:06:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則 你必死無疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.28,0:06:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙人\N連志志雄真實都打不贏劍心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.25,0:06:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.26,0:06:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可是好不容易\N才救回一命的重傷患呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.36,0:07:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他受傷的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.53,0:07:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始就被\N宣告死亡的白石被殺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.34,0:07:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是第三個如預告所指的\N死掉的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.94,0:07:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按照調查\N這三人都是德川統治時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.48,0:07:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取締天主教的急先鋒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天主教？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.52,0:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維新以前\N天主教是被嚴格查禁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼 我聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.49,0:07:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德川時代\N信天主教的人都受到嚴格處罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連女人、小孩在內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.16,0:07:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是信徒們\N依然偷偷保護她們的信仰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 那是報仇嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.64,0:07:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 傳說中的劍士天草翔伍\N他的意圖至今仍然不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.81,0:07:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想一切恐怕才剛剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.85,0:07:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.96,0:08:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該躺下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.66,0:08:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是說那個時候\N比古師父傳來聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.76,0:08:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.66,0:08:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教天草翔伍\N飛天御劍流的人還活在世間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.65,0:09:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信心深厚的兄弟們\N神祝福你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.62,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神賜予心靈純潔的人幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神賜予幸福…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神賜予心靈貧瘠的人幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.60,0:09:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神賜予幸福…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人在幹什麼呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.24,0:09:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信心深厚的人啊\N神與你們同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.18,0:09:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神與我們同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.52,0:09:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我給你們幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.63,0:09:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發誓實現神國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要毫無畏懼地遵從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神國是屬於你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.54,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多麼高貴呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.80,0:10:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真像聖母瑪莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.27,0:10:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是聖母 她是活女神\N聖母呀 聖母呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女人到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要查出那女人的真實身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.23,0:10:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用理他們 走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.60,0:11:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有何貴幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有何貴幹？\N這是什麼問候語啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.64,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可是來給\N謠傳的聖母拜拜的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.18,0:11:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是人人都能走的大路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.88,0:11:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你們是警察\N也沒權利阻擾無罪的人通行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.19,0:11:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 莊三 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.52,0:11:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.12,0:11:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 確認有沒有罪\N正是我們的工作呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人通報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.77,0:11:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這附近在舉行可疑聚會哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.68,0:11:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以 莊三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.75,0:11:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒要看你能忍耐到何時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.72,0:11:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常痛跟有點痛\N你喜歡哪一種啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.66,0:12:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.16,0:12:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你敢反抗警察 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就讓你們痛死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.77,0:12:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不堪一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.18,0:12:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.32,0:12:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了你 怎麼這麼暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.62,0:12:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莊三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.22,0:12:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 肋骨、肩膀\N手臂骨頭都受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頂多只能治到讓他們走路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.03,0:12:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之\N先找東西把骨頭固定起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.37,0:12:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 這女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手 莊三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.71,0:12:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會放過你們的\N你們給我記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.84,0:12:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要躺到什麼時候\N快起來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.21,0:12:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可愛 誰怕誰了 要來就來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼 我是好心幫助人的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.92,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在製造麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.79,0:13:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若要用暴力來解決\N由莊三出手就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.26,0:13:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 被官府的人盯上以後\N事情就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.33,0:13:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 我知道 我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.71,0:13:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼嘛 我可是好心\N把這東西搶回來給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.48,0:13:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.08,0:13:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不玩了 辛苦把東西搶回來\N連句感謝都得不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾脆\N把這東西賣給古董店算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.45,0:13:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話先講明 我頭一次\N碰到像你這種高傲的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼 站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.86,0:13:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那個墜子還過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.20,0:13:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,墜子？這東西那麼重要嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要就用搶的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先打倒我 再慢慢去拿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.81,0:14:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.43,0:14:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事 沒打中就裂開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.96,0:14:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是頭一個連續三次\N避開我的火龍絕招的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.00,0:14:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法 雖然骨頭沒完全好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.88,0:14:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 別跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.05,0:14:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的決鬥還沒結束 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.66,0:14:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得了吧 要你自以為是在挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.73,0:14:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是 憑你這樣子\N怎麼避過我的拳頭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 先暫停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.61,0:15:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 有夠倒霉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.82,0:15:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼當時我不還給他\N要賭那口氣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我濫用暴力嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仁志田兵衛是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.86,0:16:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大陸將飛天御劍流\N傳授給天草翔伍的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.93,0:16:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來他回到日本隱居起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在因為宿疾惡化 來日不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.91,0:16:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是突然接到他連絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問仁志田兵衛在家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.66,0:17:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您就是仁志田兵衛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是緋村劍心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.00,0:17:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.20,0:17:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如你所見 我時間所剩不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.94,0:17:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得趁一口氣還在時\N將一切都說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.61,0:17:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都跟三人被殺\N只是一個小小的開端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.88,0:18:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過不久\N島原可能會發生大動亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,島原？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.82,0:18:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對天草翔伍越過250年的時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.66,0:18:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想在島原再度興亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.90,0:18:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞現在的政府\N築起神的國度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.50,0:18:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神的國家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.01,0:18:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵衛大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.74,0:18:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍確實是天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.98,0:18:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一度這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.21,0:18:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將天主教徒的未來\N托付給當時還是少年的翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.75,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…\N一切遠遠超出我的預料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.93,0:18:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 翔伍\N不可以 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.36,0:18:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼做違反神的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.73,0:18:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管 我發誓要報仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.30,0:18:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了替那些\N被虐待而死的數萬人們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.91,0:18:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總有一天\N我要回到日本破壞一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後為我的同胞創造神的國度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.91,0:19:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說\N神不可能允許那種事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.05,0:19:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的那種神我不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.06,0:19:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.39,0:19:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵衛 以前你提過\N飛天御劍流的維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫做緋村是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要以這把傳說中的神劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去打敗那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.24,0:19:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超越飛天御劍流\N的真正的御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將屬於這把劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就要成為神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.22,0:19:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍 看來我把飛天御劍流\N傳授給你是錯誤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必需有個人來阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.18,0:20:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那以後我的眼睛就永遠失明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.02,0:20:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.19,0:20:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是當時翔伍使出的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.33,0:20:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是從飛天御劍流開闢以來\N頭一個加入的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.83,0:20:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個天才完成了這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.44,0:20:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心\N現在不阻止天草翔伍的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.81,0:20:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本可能會發生\N難以想像的悲劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.58,0:20:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有辦法阻止翔伍的人除了你…\N除了你以外…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵衛大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.82,0:20:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵衛大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作一點 兵衛大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.59,0:20:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才他來過這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.13,0:21:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最後一次傾全力說服他\N結果一樣無效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.10,0:21:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了 劍心 你要阻止…翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵衛大人兵衛大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.95,0:22:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心 我在島原等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.06,0:22:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍

